summary:
Target conscious, focussed and effective!

I’m actively involved in and focused on setting and achieving organizational goals. In addition, I set high standards and I want to deliver excellent performance. 

Reliability and openness are of tremendous importance to me. I’m clear about what I can deliver. In this way colleagues and relations can count on me. I get motivated by involvement in devising and deploying concepts where I pay a lot of attention to processes.

I get my energy from initiating, planning and following up on projects. In complex situations I intuitively see in which direction the solution should be sought. Within processes I see the broad outlines and analyze them in detail in order to achieve the desired results.

source: Personality survey written by: MariekeWesselman, Development Platform for coaches & consultants OPcc.
